# Examples

This folder contains practical examples of defensive programming and debugging techniques.

## Files
1. [try_except.py](./try_except.py): Demonstrates the use of `try-except` blocks for error handling.
2. [runtime_error.py](./runtime_error.py): Shows how to handle runtime errors.
3. [logical_error.py](./logical_error.py): Illustrates how to identify and fix logical errors.

---

Explore these examples to see defensive programming and debugging in action!
